<p><b>Justice</b> is the concept of <a href="/wiki/Morality" title="Morality">moral</a> rightness based on <a href="/wiki/Ethics" title="Ethics">ethics</a>, <a href="/wiki/Rationality" title="Rationality">rationality</a>, <a href="/wiki/Law" title="Law">law</a>, <a href="/wiki/Natural_law" title="Natural law">natural law</a>, <a href="/wiki/Fairness" title="Fairness">fairness</a> and <a href="/wiki/Equity" title="Equity">equity</a>."<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
